All translations included in this repository are public domain works in the
United States, as documented in each text's YAML frontmatter (translator and
translation year).

Splits, groupings, structural editing decisions, and the library.json index
schema are released under CC0 1.0 (public domain dedication):
https://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/

This means anyone can use the splits and structure for any purpose, with or
without attribution.
